Character:

-could have a character that requires a few copies of it to become a character

Potential skills:

-stockpile - has food to eat to get HP back up or remove status ailment
-swift - resolves ties as attacker being winner
-cause ailment
-card draw(s)
-allows to destroy a card after an attack
-strength against X trait

Equipment:

Most equipment will add some sort of energy to the pool

-boost DEF/ATT
-cause poison/burn/dizzy on attack/defend
-prevent poison/burn/dizzy
-lower amount of energy needed

Spell:

Option to make any card stay with energy attached

-poison/burn/dizzy opponent character
-cards that add X amount of energy to the game
-boost DEF/ATT
-draw card from discard/grave
-draw X amount of cards from deck
-add another card draw at beginning of turn
-add another card draw at final stage of turn
-destroy opponent equipment/spell
-antidote to remove status ailment
-add more HP

Trigger:

-probably same as spells... not sure yet

